===Noun===

{{en-noun}}

# A type of [[machine tool]] invented during the World War I era 
to expedite the quick-yet-precise location of hole centers. It was originally developed to expedite the making of drill jigs, but its capabilities lent themselves to any precise-hole-location task, and its principles helped advance machine tool technology toward later NC and CNC development.

